{"tid":2488543,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「娛賓」女記者女廁採訪變「拒捕」 辯方斥警濫權  胡椒噴霧「噴完一支又一支」","createTime":"2021-04-14T10:01:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T10:16:35.000Z","uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5ff9328abf6f408a2a38b04a6da7948cd2823852","tid":2488543,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:01:59.000Z","msg":"網媒「娛賓」一名女記者去年母親節深夜採訪期間，在公園公廁疑遭防暴警施用暴力，包括跪頸及以胡椒噴霧「噴完一支又一支」，女記者一度休克及失禁，最終反被控抗拒警員執行職務，案件今續審。警長稱女記者案發時推女警，頑強抵抗，又不理他及女警警告，在別無選擇下使用最低武力，兩度向女記者噴胡椒噴霧，否認對女記者用不合法武力。<br />\n<br />\n案件由主任裁判官<span class=\"red\">嚴舜儀</span>審理。女被告何（27歲）被控於去年5月11日，在旺角洗衣街花園公廁的女廁內，抗拒在正當執行職務的警務人員，分別為女警18366劉曦晨、警長58604徐啟迪、警員18258鄭相平，以及警員24262李廸燊。<br />\n<br />\n徐警告「男子」稱：「警察！唔好郁！否則使用胡椒噴劑！」惟對方沒有理會，繼續衝向公廁出入口，他立即施放胡椒噴劑約一秒，<span class=\"red\">將對方拖回廁所</span>，對方失重心跌到地上。<br />\n徐再指，被告被制服<span class=\"red\">後頭撼地面，出現自殘行為</span>，且不斷掙扎，<span class=\"red\">他才再次向被告噴胡椒噴霧</span>。<br />\n<br />\n徐同意<span class=\"red\">當時並非以拒抗警員罪拘捕</span>及警誡被告，惟解釋指用甚麼控罪拘捕被告非首要考慮。被告「中椒」後額頭紅腫，由一男一女警員押送至醫院，徐自言事後亦到醫院，以確保被告及同袍安全。<br />\n<br />\n辯方則質疑，警長與同袍到醫院是包藏禍心，因他們知悉已闖禍，沒理由如此對待記者。"},{"pid":"1807a9fe194e69eb6efee687c0554df0ded576d8","tid":2488543,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:02:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/Z6FFKXG3JFHQBD3KS6BLVD4XY4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FZ6FFKXG3JFHQBD3KS6BLVD4XY4%2F&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvrQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=844096ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FZ6FFKXG3JFHQBD3KS6BLVD4XY4%2F&h=6c29e372\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/Z6FFKXG3JFHQBD3KS6BLVD4XY4/</a>"},{"pid":"07e43fdaad3ac74ddeaaa1f42f2822ab93125f8c","tid":2488543,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:05:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f299d2bb18cd4fae163702e80fd33c836b4cd4b","tid":2488543,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:07:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c5988dea68903b6bbf5537b9d4adc13b2813e8","tid":2488543,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:08:11.000Z","msg":"佢受傷噴多兩下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />噴暈佢咩"},{"pid":"b9e151c9aea66433f90146fc56311a69e255f462","tid":2488543,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:13:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa4f98286fbf49fd6d78ed5fb35639788850b2de","tid":2488543,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}